==Tatar==
===Etymology===
Akin to Old English '''bilang''' - ''belong'' ( '''bi''', ''be'' + '''lang''', ''along with)''.

#''Etymological spelling:'' '''belang'''
#''Phonetic spelling:'' '''belang''', '''belyang'''

===Conjunction===
'''belang'''
#[[belong]], [[with]]
#:Curd '''belang''' a pie (''curd belyan ei pai'') = A pie '''belong''' with curd ''(curd pie, curd tart, cheese-cake)

